[ACTIVITY] 訂單處理流程
[ACTOR] 客戶 -> {specs/actors/客戶.md}
[ACTOR] 系統 -> {specs/actors/系統.md}
[ACTOR] 倉庫 -> {specs/actors/倉庫.md}
[ACTOR] 金流 -> {specs/actors/金流.md}

[INITIAL]
[STEP:1] @客戶 {specs/commands/提交訂單.feature}
[STEP:2] @系統 {specs/queries/驗證訂單.feature}
[DECISION:2a] 訂單是否有效
  [BRANCH:2a:有效]
    [STEP:2a.1] @客戶 {specs/ui/顯示確認頁.md}
    [DECISION:2a1] 是否使用優惠券
      [BRANCH:2a1:是]
        [STEP:2a1.1] @系統 {specs/commands/套用優惠券.feature}
        [DECISION:2a1a] 優惠券是否有效
          [BRANCH:2a1a:有效]
            [STEP:2a1a.1] @客戶 {specs/ui/顯示折扣金額.md}
          [BRANCH:2a1a:過期]
            [STEP:2a1a.2] @客戶 {specs/ui/優惠券過期提示.md}
          [BRANCH:2a1a:已用]
            [STEP:2a1a.3] @客戶 {specs/ui/優惠券已使用提示.md}
        [MERGE:2a1a]
      [BRANCH:2a1:否]
        [STEP:2a1.2] @客戶 {specs/ui/顯示原價.md}
    [MERGE:2a1]
  [BRANCH:2a:無效]
    [STEP:2a.2] @客戶 {specs/ui/顯示錯誤訊息.md}
    [DECISION:2a2] 錯誤類型
      [BRANCH:2a2:庫存不足]
        [STEP:2a2.1] @客戶 {specs/ui/建議替代商品.md}
      [BRANCH:2a2:地址無效]
        [STEP:2a2.2] @客戶 {specs/ui/地址修正表單.md}
      [BRANCH:2a2:else]
        [STEP:2a2.3] @客戶 {specs/ui/聯繫客服.md}
    [MERGE:2a2]
[MERGE:2a]

[STEP:3] @金流 {specs/commands/處理付款.feature}
[FORK:3a]
  [PARALLEL:3a]
    [STEP:3a.1] @金流 {specs/commands/扣款.feature}
    [DECISION:3a1] 扣款結果
      [BRANCH:3a1:成功]
        [STEP:3a1.1] @系統 {specs/commands/記錄交易.feature}
      [BRANCH:3a1:失敗]
        [STEP:3a1.2] @系統 {specs/commands/標記付款失敗.feature}
    [MERGE:3a1]
  [PARALLEL:3a]
    [STEP:3a.2] @系統 {specs/commands/鎖定庫存.feature}
  [PARALLEL:3a]
    [STEP:3a.3] @系統 {specs/commands/發送確認信.feature}
[JOIN:3a]

[STEP:4] @倉庫 {specs/commands/準備出貨.feature}
[FORK:4a]
  [PARALLEL:4a]
    [STEP:4a.1] @倉庫 {specs/commands/揀貨.feature}
  [PARALLEL:4a]
    [STEP:4a.2] @倉庫 {specs/commands/包裝.feature}
    [DECISION:4a1] 是否需要禮品包裝
      [BRANCH:4a1:是]
        [STEP:4a1.1] @倉庫 {specs/commands/禮品包裝.feature}
      [BRANCH:4a1:否]
        [STEP:4a1.2] @倉庫 {specs/commands/標準包裝.feature}
    [MERGE:4a1]
  [PARALLEL:4a]
    [STEP:4a.3] @系統 {specs/commands/更新訂單狀態.feature}
[JOIN:4a]

[STEP:5] @系統 {specs/commands/完成訂單.feature}
[FINAL]
